PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FA mother who forced a vulnerable woman
OL,7,Fto work as a slave in her house for
OL,8,Fmore than 25 years has been sentenced
OL,9,Fto 13 years in prison.
OL,11,FThe woman, who ITV News is calling K,
OL,12,Fwas 16 when she moved into the squalid
OL,13,Fhome of mother-of-10 Amanda Wixon, 56,
OL,14,Fin 1995 and remained there until 2021.
OL,16,FWixon, aged 56, forced K to do manual
OL,17,Flabour, regularly assaulted her and
OL,18,Fdeprived her of food and healthcare.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FThe victim was finally freed in March
OL,7,F2021 after police went to the house in
OL,8,Fresponse to a report made by one of
OL,9,FWixon's sons. She is now in her 40s.
OL,11,FIn a victim statement read during the
OL,12,Fsentencing of Wixon, K wrote that she
OL,13,Fstill lives with "trauma and
OL,14,Fnightmares" every day.
OL,16,FHer foster mother has told ITV news
OL,17,Fshe is "constantly living in fear"
OL,18,Fafter the ordeal.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FDuring a trial, Gloucester Crown Court
OL,7,Fheard the woman was regularly beaten
OL,8,Fand also hit with a broom handle `
OL,9,Fknocking out her teeth.
OL,11,FThe moment Amanda Wixon was arrested
OL,12,Fby police officers
OL,14,FWashing-up liquid would be squirted
OL,15,Fdown her throat, bleach splashed on
OL,16,Fher face, and she had her head
OL,17,Frepeatedly shaved against her will.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
