FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FK's food was limited by Wixon, and she
OL,7,Flived off scraps, could not leave the
OL,8,Fhouse and was forced to secretly wash
OL,9,Fat night.
OL,11,FWhen they arrived at the house, in the
OL,12,FPriors Park area of Tewkesbury,
OL,13,Fofficers described the woman's bedroom
OL,14,Fas looking like a "prison cell", with
OL,15,Fother bedrooms untidy and dirty.
OL,17,FShe told officers: "I don't want to be
OL,18,Fhere. I don't feel safe. Mandy hits me
OL,19,Fall the time. I don't like it. I
OL,20,Fhaven't washed for years. She doesn't
OL,21,Flet me."
OL,26,@vD@SOUvD@_O]yD@TOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
