PN,43705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FWixon denied a charge of false
OL,7,Fimprisonment, two charges of requiring
OL,8,Fa person to perform forced or
OL,9,Fcompulsory labour, and four charges of
OL,10,Fassault occasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,12,FA jury acquitted her of one assault
OL,13,Fcharge but found her guilty of the
OL,14,Fothers.
OL,16,F'For 25 years I lived in fear'
OL,18,FDuring the sentencing hearing of Wixon
OL,19,Fat Gloucester Crown Court, Sam Jones,
OL,20,Fprosecuting, read a note the victim
OL,21,Fhad written to the court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FThe woman, who is not being
OL,7,Fidentified, said: "For 25 years, I
OL,8,Flived in fear, control and abuse. I
OL,9,Fwas treated as though my life, my
OL,10,Ffreedom and my voice did not matter.
OL,12,F"Although my abuser has now been found
OL,13,Fguilty, the trauma and the nightmares
OL,14,Fare something I still carry with me
OL,15,Fevery day.
OL,17,F"I am now living with a wonderful
OL,18,Ffamily who show me kindness, patience
OL,19,Fand support.
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,F"Their love is helping me slowly
OL,7,Frebuild the life that was taken from
OL,8,Fme and begin to feel safe again.
OL,10,F"Nothing can give me back the 25 years
OL,11,FI lost. But I hope the court
OL,12,Frecognises the deep and lasting harm
OL,13,Fthis abuse has caused and delivers a
OL,14,Fsentence that truly reflects the
OL,15,Fseriousness of these crimes."
OL,17,F'Wixon didn't see her as a human being'
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
