OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FDetectives leading on the case say
OL,7,FWixon was not known to the police
OL,8,Fprior to her arrest and would portray
OL,9,Fherself as a member of the community
OL,10,Fwho volunteered and helped others.
OL,12,F"On the outside she shows a caring,
OL,13,Floving person towards her own
OL,14,Fchildren", said Detective
OL,15,FSuperintendent Ian Fletcher from
OL,16,FGloucestershire Police.
OL,18,F"But on the inside, she had this dark
OL,19,Fsecret that she had a slave living
OL,20,Finside her property."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FDetective Superintendent said K was
OL,7,F"completely dehumanised" by Wixon
OL,8,Fthroughout the 25-year period.
OL,10,F"(We found her in a) very poor
OL,11,Fcondition", he said. "She had,
OL,12,Fabscesses in her teeth, callouses
OL,13,Facross her feet, she was severely
OL,14,Fmalnourished and she was in a very,
OL,15,Fvery bad state.
OL,17,F"Amanda was a family friend. And she'd
OL,18,Ftaken her into her property, seemingly
OL,19,Fto sort of care for her. And I
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,Fthink our victim probably thought that
OL,7,Fshe was going to be looked after.
OL,9,F"But it seems, quite quickly, that
OL,10,FAmanda Wixon had taken her benefits
OL,11,Foff her and made sure they were paid
OL,12,Fstraight to her.
OL,14,F"Our victim was totally dehumanised. I
OL,15,Fdon't think Amanda Wixon saw her as
OL,16,Fbeing a human being. She saw her as a
OL,17,Fslave to use for her own will to make
OL,18,Fher life better. She was treated very,
OL,19,Fvery differently to Amanda's own
OL,20,Fchildren."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FThe detective went on to say that K
OL,7,Fwas expected to care for the children,
OL,8,Fby washing them and getting them ready
OL,9,Ffor school, but she received no care
OL,10,Fherself.
OL,12,FHe continued: "She wanted long hair,
OL,13,Fand Wixon cut her hair off. She (K)
OL,14,Fwould try to wash her hair and then
OL,15,Fwhen Wixon discovered that it had been
OL,16,Fwashed, she would threaten and beat
OL,17,Fher again in those scenarios, and
OL,18,Fultimately, she ended up shaving her
OL,19,Fhair off to ensure that she couldn't
OL,20,Fhave that long hair and clean hair
OL,21,Fthat she wanted."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
