OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,FK 'dreamt of seeing sunlight', says
OL,7,Fdetective
OL,9,FThe detective said one of K's 'dreams
OL,10,Fwas to see sunlight'; something Wixon
OL,11,Fprevented her from each day she was
OL,12,Fheld captive.
OL,14,FHe said that Wixon would put "black
OL,15,Fbin liners over the windows" to stop
OL,16,Fher from seeing outside.
OL,18,FThe detective said K is now leading a
OL,19,Fbetter and safer life but every day
OL,20,Flives with the trauma of what she was
OL,21,Fput through.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1773436322
OL,3,CMother who imprisoned, beat and abused
OL,4,Cvulnerable woman for 25 years jailed
OL,6,F"She's now got a caring person looking
OL,7,Fafter her. She's got her own room, but
OL,8,Fshe is still suffering quite badly
OL,9,Ffrom those traumatic events", he said.
OL,11,F"She has flashbacks, where she fears
OL,12,Fthat Wixon is in her room and is
OL,13,Finvading her life now. She has got a
OL,14,Fcaring environment around her, but
OL,15,Fthis is going to cause a significant
OL,16,Ftrauma, probably for the rest of her
OL,17,Flife", he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
